 r‚Üê{ns}Diff y;rc;more;path;‚éïTRAP;short;space;folder;buff;cmd
‚çù Returns a diff for all changes either...
‚çù * staged
‚çù * in the working area
‚çù * all changes
‚çù r is a matrix with two columns and zero or more rows.
‚çù `y` must be one of:
‚çù   * Fully qualfied name of a namespace  that is an opened Cider project
‚çù   * Fully qualified path to a Git-managed project
 ‚éïTRAP‚Üê(811 'E' '‚éïDMX.EM ‚éïsignal 811')(0 'N')
 ns‚Üê{0<‚éïNC ‚çµ:‚çé‚çµ ‚ãÑ ns‚Üê‚éïNS'' ‚ãÑ ns.op‚Üê'all' ‚ãÑ ns}'ns'
 (space folder)‚ÜêEstablishProject y
 cmd‚Üê'diff'
 :Select ‚éïC ns.op
 :Case 'stage'
     cmd,‚Üê' --staged'
 :Case 'work'
         ‚çù No action required
 :Case 'all'
     cmd,‚Üê' HEAD'
 :EndSelect
 (rc more r)‚Üêfolder U.RunGitCommand cmd
 more U.Assert 0=rc
‚çùDone
